No. 11-630. T. A., Petitioner v. Forest Grove School District. 565 U.S. 1185, 132 S. Ct. 1145, 2012 U.S. LEXIS 1033.

181 L. Ed. 2d 1031,

January 23, 2012.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied. Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 638 F.3d 1234.
